"I believe that thanks to our initiative now all the inhabitants have a certain link with this building.
Everyone knows his book is part of the library.
Even though he's just there to decorate.
In this way, the MVRDV study has achieved a complete success in this queen discipline, which in the specialized argot is known as "creation of an identity".
The city of Spijkenisse has written a piece of the history of literature.
Regardless of how young and uneducated it may be.
Finally, a starting point for conforming your identity.
